rows.label: tlk70000068_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Iira is so much more than I realized
it was.

rows.label: tlk70000068_04_msg0002
rows.name:
I liked the sparkly ball that was at the
top of the royal palace, but it's gone
now.

rows.label: tlk70000068_04_msg0003
rows.name:
There's so much I don't know! About
my dad's job, about Iira...

rows.label: tlk70000068_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Would it change anything if I did know
more? I wonder if there's really much
a guy like me can do...

rows.label: tlk70000068_04_msg0005
rows.name:
I don't know much about this, either,
but I think I want to change. I want to
do something for Iira.
